codex
The statistical pass is complete. The strongest signal is not broad benefit from most treatments; it is a large palbociclib interaction pattern, especially better PFS in ER-positive disease and worse relative benefit in PIK3CA-mutant or high-Ki67 groups. I’m now turning those tested findings into the required transcript and narrative files.
